{"tid":1488631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【跪求】求下大家正確使用twitter，唔好成為我哋自己都唔鐘意嘅spam bot","createTime":"2019-08-19T16:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T17:10:02.000Z","uid":35215,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c207d6d580125d3b5a1fbeaaac334fedead5dcbc","tid":1488631,"uid":35215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"（代post）<br />\n<br />\n呢排外國文宣組真係好撚勁，reddit同twitter都推到香港嘅事上國際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係有大量人註冊啲新account，又冇去了解到twitter同連登一樣，其實都有自己一套規矩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲twitter用家開始俾人鳩 tag：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0N3GR6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0N3GR6h.jpg&h=c603d1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係twitter tg谷嘅少少建議，求下大家睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTG group：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">小心唔好提起TG group，你會成為人地眼中嘅三毛</span></strong><br />\npo你條tweet嘅link上嚟我哋幫推<br />\n但share都要FC，搵下個source，睇下佢平時可唔可信<br />\n<br />\nTwitter 101：<br />\n- 加pro pic同bio簡介，唔好成個bot咁<br />\n- 一撚定要加hashtag，唔用你條tweet跟本冇人睇，之後會講用咩tag<br />\n- Retweet人地嘅嘢去發放資訊<br />\n- Quote Retweet去加自己意見<br />\n<br />\n點係一條好tweet?<br />\n- Retweet都要FC，睇佢哋係咪可信嘅account<br />\n- 有圖有片有真相<br />\n- 太長啲人會TLDR<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">4個hashtag盡晒，唔好再多</span></strong><br />\n- 唔好加啲唔關事嘅hashtag<br />\n- <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好亂鳩咁tag唔識嘅人</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可用hashtag：<br />\n#FreedomHK #HongKong #HongKongProtests #FreeHK #antiELAB #HKProtests #HongKongers #PrayforHongKong #StandwithHK #FightforFreedom<br />\n<br />\n嚟加入tg大家庭：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NKR92Fj9_oId62sw06k0XQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNKR92Fj9_oId62sw06k0XQ&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=5994203b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NKR92Fj9_oId62sw06k0XQ</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度有條list話你知有咩account可以follow：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chercywong/lists/stand-with-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchercywong%2Flists%2Fstand-with-hong-kong&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAOIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=f3663f26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chercywong/lists/stand-with-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家注意少少，見手足俾人屌我都覺得好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b25a5c7c73a22642e78f828196aec45a0f4438d","tid":1488631,"uid":24944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"ac39b1f4ec8ef012d657ab82a4ef7d000379f3bc","tid":1488631,"uid":230942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"正確使用Twitter 正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353aef98826cc62404a70ca43e37bf4415d15ac0","tid":1488631,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:19:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"05c5d95afd363702103eee3058eac14849d78032","tid":1488631,"uid":63437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:19:54.000Z","msg":"唔緊要， 大家都係第一次，學下就識架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a2d2984e27f44dccf05223536d8f5e61dc7f8e","tid":1488631,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"推到一人一twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f16783a0e65ba3f6f60b70d513241049f673be8","tid":1488631,"uid":137265,"like":0