 />\n唔知有幾多人有幫手推呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就由10點推到11點半左右<br />\n觀鳥找數咁多人去現場<br />\n文宣呢啲正經野 幾時肯幫手呢<br />\nTwitter啊 要開返個 肯開未<br />\n<br />\n真係嬲架 玩完喇 做正經野喇幫手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"唔係開post 講一句 文宣做野 就完<br />\n人人手上有一部電話 都做到文宣<br />\n希望大家善用twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完"},{"pid":"c5a073db1d242d9b1abb9f78417c9d7e7ef1de68","tid":1488631,"uid":115212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"見埋改返個 username<br />\n有外國人話一見到個名後面有一串 random number (e.g. Carrie201903718) 就覺得嗰個係 bot/ spam<br />\n麻煩各位去一去 Setting and Privacy &gt; Account &gt; User Name 改走串 random number<br />\n<br />\n呢外 retweet 都加一兩句短短哋嘅 comments，唔好淨係得幾個 hashtags，唔係好似 bot"},{"pid":"9b2a06e0479273bb84e1dfbcf291bbdf48083fc6","tid":1488631,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"bb16aae77d7682a77905e5f4fc8e1c5bc73586d3","tid":1488631,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9c62920b190f9fab6180b88f2ae00a92e335b93","tid":1488631,"uid":128333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f477f50edc1589b2dca086f4def83ce86b971e51","tid":1488631,"uid":69525,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩10點推hastag<br />\n唔知有幾多人有幫手推呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就由10點推到11點半左右<br />\n觀鳥找數咁多人去現場<br />\n文宣呢啲正經野 幾時肯幫手呢<br />\nTwitter啊 要開返個 肯開未<br />\n<br />\n真係嬲架 玩完喇 做正經野喇幫手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"我十點推到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦了 我沖完涼繼續推"},{"pid":"5bd852ef74a64cf37f221891cf8b5080989d9472","tid":1488631,"uid":115212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5a073db1d242d9b1abb9f78417c9d7e7ef1de68","tid":1488631,"uid":115212,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"見埋改返個 username<br />\n有外國人話一見到個名後面有一串 random number (e.g. Carrie201903718) 就覺得嗰個係 bot/ spam<br />\n麻煩各位去一去 Setting and Privacy &gt; Account &gt; User Name 改走串 random number<br />\n<br />\n呢外 retweet 都加一兩句短短哋嘅 comments，唔好淨係得幾個 hashtags，唔係好似 bot"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"*同埋<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c2bf5d899e667178c5eaa6c898bddf44b99ce0","tid":1488631,"uid":72916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"推！講得好 慢慢學習"},{"pid":"dab13f190f51379e2c12ba9f59a5ae482ac68903","tid":1488631,"uid":72222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa08e5a743b23408725b852c0fcd63230896ac13","tid":1488631,"uid":278787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"tui ah tui yueng jei post tui"},{"pid":"b719f0035a9abf4540b7492a9a86fbf7a70c369e","tid":1488631,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"小心啲 唔好做豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8debde4df855736e3c00d3d0ed19b8e82a4ea3c","tid":1488631,"uid":270078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"62a3445944ee3b979ad3e4912e14ebe4cfad43eb","tid":1488631,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:25:36.000Z","msg":"當真account咁玩就最正確<br />\n當我地笑Chinese troll嘅時候，更加唔好做同一樣野"},{"pid":"30ba70893e2108386905fe4f7b0010e709c281c5","tid":1488631,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"入鄉隨俗嘛"},{"pid":"ee8913649eb357240a66e940f018f2af9b33c1a2","tid":1488631,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488148\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488148</a><br />\n<br />\n經過琴日之後，外國多咗好多人留意香港<br />\n我地要食住個勢，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">connect埋外國人</span></span>！<br />\n就咁講5大訴求係唔夠，外國人好難用同理心去幫我地<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">所以我地要運用返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢地認同嘅價值觀同埋理念</span>！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">將'香港人'英文 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">'Hong Konger' 變成代表勇氣同埋自由嘅人</span></strong><br />\n大家都可以係Hong Konger!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家幫手宣傳<br />\n用facebook, ig, twitter, 去令到 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#WeAreHongKonger</span></span></strong>變成trend<br />\nconnect更多外國人去幫我地！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c41hpLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc41hpLQ.jpg&h=503a1256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以嘅請同時share埋呢段文字：<br />\n<br />\nPlease forward:<br />\n<br />\nHong Kongers have demonstrated utmost perseverance and determination to bravely pursue freedom under authoritarianism.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Hong Konger&quot; is no longer defined by where one is located. &quot;Hong Konger&quot; represents people who value 'courage' and 'freedom'. We sincerely hope every one who upholds this exact same belief can show your support to all Hong Kongers by sharing the tag #WeAreHongKonger on social media. <br />\n<br />\nFrom now on, people who    love freedom and courage are all &quot;Hong Konger&quot;, no matter who you are, where you are from.<br />\n<br />\n#WeAreHongKonger<br />\n<br />\n請轉發：<br />\n香港人已經展示出無比的堅毅和決心，在強權之下，仍勇敢地追求自由。<br />\n<br />\n香港人不再是地域上的觀念，而是代表「勇氣」和「自由」，希望世界每一位堅持同一信念的人，用你任何的方法表達對香港人的支持，放上你的社交媒體，並 #WeAreHongKonger。<br />\n<br />\n從今以後，再沒有人種界限，也沒有國界，只有熱愛自由和勇敢的Hong Konger。<br />\n<br />\n#WeAreHongKonger"},{"pid":"115721ec8a72f0a75eb1c833c69e18698bfef620","tid":1488631,"uid":123274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:25:56.000Z","msg":"最重要係大家留comment講下自己睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caeb5db990433e9871871ba4618918adf8003727","tid":1488631,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8db47668ed7f96e60787253ac005a677010f52f","tid":1488631,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f477f50edc1589b2dca086f4def83ce86b971e51","tid":1488631,"uid":69525,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩10點推hastag<br />\n唔知有幾多人有幫手推呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己就由10點推到11點半左右<br />\n觀鳥找數咁多人去現場<br />\n文宣呢啲正經野 幾時肯幫手呢<br />\nTwitter啊 要開返個 肯開未<br />\n<br />\n真係嬲架 玩完喇 做正經野喇幫手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:28:17.000Z","msg":"玩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87372136f370048a686cd23673a6d8d36d9935e2","tid":1488631,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8db47668ed7f96e60787253ac005a677010f52f","tid":1488631,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f477f50edc1589b2dca086f4def83ce86b971e51","tid":1488631,"uid":69525,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"岩岩10點推hastag<br />\n唔知有幾多人有幫手推呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /